work_description: BG Corp - Free to Backload Report
comments:
Mr. Walli was unable to find the trucks that were recently booked. To identify and resolve the issue, we followed these steps:
1) Analyzed the SQL connection.
2) Checked the refresh history.
3) Verified the data in Power BI against the data stored in SQL.
4) Re-examined the filters applied in the report.
5) Identified the root cause: The issue was with the Corridor column from the Route table. It should have contained "Dar es Salaam," but the missing trucks had this field left blank.
6) After communicating this to Mr. Walli, he confirmed that he would address it further.
